snippet.title: NATURAL JUICE | Red Tender Coconut Sarbath | Healthy Juice Making in Village | Summer Health Drinks
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we make our village traditional sarbath juice with farm-fresh King Coconut! Tender Coconut water is most effective in summer season. King Coconut variant is a very rare variant than a normal coconut!

We add basil seeds and King coconut meat to make this juice as healthy drink! The taste is divine!

snippet.title: Oppenheimer | New Trailer
snippet.description:
Oppenheimer - Only In Theaters 7 21 23

Written and directed by Christopher Nolan, Oppenheimer is an IMAX¬Æ-shot epic thriller that thrusts audiences into the pulse-pounding paradox of the enigmatic man who must risk destroying the world in order to save it. 
 
The film stars Cillian Murphy as J. Robert Oppenheimer and Emily Blunt as his wife, biologist and botanist Katherine ‚ÄúKitty‚Äù Oppenheimer. Oscar¬Æ winner Matt Damon portrays General Leslie Groves Jr., director of the Manhattan Project, and Robert Downey, Jr. plays Lewis Strauss, a founding commissioner of the U.S. Atomic Energy Commission. 
 
Academy Award¬Æ nominee Florence Pugh plays psychiatrist Jean Tatlock, Benny Safdie plays theoretical physicist Edward Teller, Michael Angarano plays Robert Serber and Josh Hartnett plays pioneering American nuclear scientist Ernest Lawrence.
 
Oppenheimer also stars Oscar¬Æ winner Rami Malek and reunites Nolan with eight-time Oscar¬Æ nominated actor, writer and filmmaker Kenneth Branagh. 
 
The cast includes Dane DeHaan (Valerian and the City of a Thousand Planets), Dylan Arnold (Halloween franchise), David Krumholtz (The Ballad of Buster Scruggs), Alden Ehrenreich (Solo: A Star Wars Story) and Matthew Modine (The Dark Knight Rises). 
 
The film is based on the Pulitzer Prize-winning book American Prometheus: The Triumph and Tragedy of J. Robert Oppenheimer by Kai Bird and the late Martin J. Sherwin. The film is produced by Emma Thomas, Atlas Entertainment‚Äôs Charles Roven and Christopher Nolan. 

Oppenheimer is filmed in a combination of IMAX¬Æ 65mm and 65mm large-format film photography including, for the first time ever, sections in IMAX¬Æ black and white analogue photography. 

Nolan‚Äôs films, including Tenet, Dunkirk, Interstellar, Inception and The Dark Knight trilogy, have earned more than $5 billion at the global box office and have been awarded 11 Oscars and 36 nominations, including two Best Picture nominations.

Batch Details : 
- We will cover Botany, Zoology, Physics, Organic Chemistry, Inorganic Chemistry, and Physical Chemistry in One Shot

- One Shot Marathon series will start on Physics wallah - Alakh Pandey Channel on 19th April 2023

- Then, Subject wise Master MCQ Marathon series will be continue on Competition Wallah YouTube Channel on 26th April 2023

- At the end, 5 Live AITS (All India Test Series) Live Discussion on Competition Wallah YouTube Channel

- After NEET 2023 Exam, the Live Paper Discussion will also be scheduled on Competition Wallah YouTube Channel at the same day.

- Lecture notes will be available on NEET Maha Revision 2023 Batch (PW App)

- The complete course will be accessible to all the students until the NEET 2023 Exams

- Marathon Schedule will be provided in the community post of Competition Wallah YT Channel and Announcement section of the PW App

snippet.description:

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3764 - 6 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3764: Jasoos Bhide
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide begins to have concerns about Tapu's motivations and makes the decision to keep an eye on him. Bhide gets into an auto and instructs the driver to keep driving in the same direction as Tapu and Sonu's vehicle. Bhide tries to bribe the vehicle driver after he refuses to obey his commands. When Tapu and Sonu are finally spotted entering a shrine, Bhide follows them as well. Bhide runs across one of his student's parents at the temple's stairs and strikes up a conversation with him. Bhide becomes impatient because it has caused a significant diversion from his stalking. See how Bhide flees when he is going to be caught by Tapu and Sonu in the act by watching the episode!

snippet.title: Manipur: Govt issues 'shoot at sight' orders as violence flares; 9,000 people rescued
snippet.description:
The #manipur  government has issued "shoot at sight" orders as violence in the state spread to its capital Imphal. Security has been strengthened, with the deployment of 55 army columns. The Rapid Action Force has been flown in. Around 500 personnel of the Rapid Action Force, a riot control police, have been flown in. More than 9,000 people have been rescued from violence-hit areas by the security forces.

Sakhiye Saheliye Lyrics:

Sakhiye saheliye,
Gujhiye paheliye,
Mathe utte layiye chan sooraj sajaa...
Naviye naveliye,
Chandan di geliye,
Barhe piche shutt gye ne khaban vale raah....
Sakhiye saheliye,
Gujhiye paheliye,
Mathe utte layiye chan sooraj sajaa.
Akhan asmaan vall chuk k tan vekhiye,
Kandhan kaule shattan kolo shutt k tan vekhiye,
Dhup shan de utte haq rakh k tan vekhiye,
Aaja aaja layiye geet zindagi de gaa...
Sakhiye saheliye,
Gujhiye paheliye,
Mathe utte layiye chan sooraj sjaa....
Kandhan kaule, shattan kolon shutt kithe jaavana,
Murh k tan panchi ne aahlane ch aavana,
Ghuggian ne bahuta uchi sikhea na gaavana,
Buk k bathere sanu zindagi de chaa,
Naviye naveliye,
Chandan di geliye,
Barhe piche shutt gye ne khabaan vaale raah....
Kholiye jo band pyi khaban di kitab ni,
Haasyean di rutt vala mangiye hisaab ni,
Saukhe ne swaal par aukhe ne jwaab ni,
Nehrean nu deyiye jaag chananan da laa..
Sakhiye Sakhiye saheliye,
Gujhiye paheliye,
Mathe utte layiye chan sooraj sjaa....
Suk gye baghan vichon labhna ko jhalliye,
Hukaman ch rahiye bas hukaman ch chaliye,
Chappa k zameen pairan heth jo swalliye,
Nadiyan ne muk jana vich dariya...
Naviye naveliye,

Chandan di geliye,
Barhe piche shutt gye ne khabaan vaale raah....
Duniya de ranga vich apna v rang hove,
Ajj hoyie kathe fr apna eh kal hove...
Reeta te riwaaz nve ghad lvange,
Dha  k purana raag nva lyie gaa...
Sakhiye saheliye,
Naviye naveliye.
Sakhiye saheliye...
Hath farh mera lyie kafila bna,
Khat k lea de sanu nikke Nike chah,
Gujiye paheliye,
Chandan di galiye...
Fikara nu deyie fook maar k udha,
Sanu v tan thode khamb kholne Sikha...
Sakhiye saheliye,
Gujhiye paheliye...
Mathe utte lyie chan sooraj sjaa...
Hath farh mera lyie qaafila bna,
Fikara nu deyie fook maar k udha...
Naviye naveliye,
Sakhiye saheliye,
Gujhiye paheliye,

Ek hath reejhan saade ek hath chaa,
Udh jana asi khamb chuni de bna,
Dharti te pair ajj nahio lgda,
Amber v hoyea neeva neeva lgda,
Asin duniya gulaabi rang laini e ranga...

snippet.title: Manipur Violence News Updates: Shoot At Sight Orders In Extreme Conditions In Manipur | News18
snippet.description:
Manipur Violence News Updates: Shoot At Sight Orders In Extreme Conditions In Manipur | News18

Manipur Curfew Live Updates: The Indian Army on Friday said that the situation in Moreh and Kangpokpi areas was brought under control and is stable. It added that all efforts are underway to restore normalcy in Imphal and Churachandpur area. On Thursday, to contain spiraling violence in Manipur between tribals and the majority Meitei community which has displaced over 9,000 people from their villages, state government issued shoot at sight order in 'extreme cases'. Fifty-five columns of the Army and Assam Rifles had to be deployed to contain widespread rioting. Meanwhile, internet services remain suspended in Manipur for five day.

snippet.title: Episode 2 | Yuzvendra Chahal & Kuldeep Yadav | Breakfast with Champions Season 8 | @skodaindia
snippet.description:
A decade ago, Yuzi got Kuldeep caught and bowled on his first class debut. And he‚Äôs been getting under Kuldeep‚Äôs skin ever since, playing the ‚Äòsenior‚Äô card whenever convenient. Perhaps, until now‚Ä¶

What started out as this great rivalry and a competition for the same spot in the Indian white ball team, has developed into an amazing brotherhood where the two of them now are committed to bringing out the best in each other, both on and off the field.

Gaurav Kapur brings the pair together and they chat about a variety of things, including some greats of the game, TV soaps, the correlation between BWC and nuptials, the pranks they‚Äôve pulled, and why it‚Äôs time to popularize the hashtag #BechaareBowlers.

This episode of Skoda presents Breakfast with Champions tastes best with a garama-garam KUL-CHA, some chholey, and a side of pyaaz, diced with a sharp CHA-KU.

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: Thousands participate in 'Tribal Solidarity March' in Manipur
snippet.description:
Thousands of people took part in the 'Tribal Solidarity March' called by a student body in Manipur. They raised slogans opposing the demand for ST status for the Meitei community. The Meiteis inhabit the Manipur valley, which constitutes about 10% of the area of the state.

snippet.title: Manipur violence: Unease over land and ST status, ground report
snippet.description:
Amid tension over the move to protect forests in the face of resistance from illegal immigrants and also the High Court's direction to include Meitei in scheduled tribes, Internet services have been suspended in the state, informed officials. The Army and Assam Rifles were deployed to control the situation in Manipur where violence broke out during a tribal agitation, a defence spokesperson said on Thursday.

Presenting the official trailer of the upcoming Bollywood movie, Chatrapathi introducing Bellamkonda Sai Sreenivas. The film is directed by V.V. Vinayak, Presented by Dr. Jayantilal Gada and produced by Dhaval Jayantilal Gada and Aksshay Jayantilal Gada under Pen Studios.
